card_name: Blackwing - Vayu the Emblem of Honor
card_text: This face-up card on the field cannot be used as a Synchro Material. If this card is in the GY: You can target 1 non-Tuner "Blackwing" monster in your GY; banish both this card and that target, and if you do, Special Summon 1 "Blackwing" Synchro Monster from your Extra Deck whose Level equals the total Levels of the banished monsters, but its effects are negated.
